ld, adding they could only handle one more and that’s it because it would make for a pretty loud house. Kevin who was married to Torrei Hart filed for divorce in February 2010, citing irreconcilable differences. Hart requested joint custody of their two children, a daughter, and a son. The divorce was finalized in November 2011. Kevin Hart and his wife have had their own issues. On December 15, 2017, Kevin admitted to having cheated on her when she was pregnant with their first son.